function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	--resolve encounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(S_ANDARIELFIGHT);
	--clear weather
	Hydra.ClearWeatherOverride(S_WORLD, S_WEATHER)
	--Play Boss Victory Music
	Hydra.MusicOverride(S_WORLD, "Music_Boss_Andariel_Victory")
	Hydra.Wait(10) -- Wait for Andariel's death animation to finish playing, then drop loot and transition to the next quest
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drorp occurs
		-- idFirstTimeRewardLocation is set/created on "Actor Killed)
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, TC_FTR_ANDARIEL, idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Campaign_Andariel")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	
end

function Start(sWorldName, sLevelAreaName)

	--Reset Music if failed
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride(S_WORLD)

end
